For now we stick with Jest because is well integrated with:

- react testing library
- screenshot testing by amex
- puppeteer

From the other hand cloudflare drops support for Jest and encourages to move to vitest.
Although its for workers, for page functions they do not have much docs & examples.

For now we stick with jest, there is no visible obstacle before moving vitest.
Once cloudflare provides dedicated config for pages(and it will be good) then we can consider move to vitest again.
